what I already know.

29:08.700 --> 29:09.655
School ain't for me.

29:09.700 --> 29:10.951
Never has been.

29:11.010 --> 29:13.478
That's an excuse,
Ralph Angel.

29:13.530 --> 29:16.829
Only teacher
ever paid me attention
was the gym coach,

29:16.880 --> 29:19.132
'cause he wanted me
to be on the track team.

29:19.190 --> 29:21.226
Rest of 'em treat me
like I can't _read
or somethIng.

29:21.280 --> 29:23.362
So you thought
that's the way
I treated you last night?

29:23.410 --> 29:25.401
Everybody do me like that.

29:25.450 --> 29:27.498
You_ain't do
nothIng new.

29:30.150 --> 29:32.710
All right.

29:34.590 --> 29:35.761
I want to apologize...

29:37.860 --> 29:39.509
for making you
feel small.

29:39.560 --> 29:40.766
And I mean that
smcerely,

29:40.820 --> 29:42.811
and I hope
you hear that.

29:42.860 --> 29:44.771
'Cause you're not small,
Ralph Angel.

29:44.820 --> 29:46.424
Man, you got a big heart,
you got a big spirit,

29:46.480 --> 29:48.471
you got a big brain.

29:48.520 --> 29:52.911
But you also got
a big case of luggage

29:52.960 --> 29:54.211
that you're carrying
around with you

29:54.270 --> 29:56.170
everywhere you go.

29:56.220 --> 29:59.098
And that makes
everything feel heavier
than it needs to be.

29:59.140 --> 30:01.745
Now, we all gotta
carry it sometimes.

