for that, too?

38:12.940 --> 38:14.498
Mm-hmm.

38:14.550 --> 38:15.972
The same rate
or better?

38:16.030 --> 38:17.327
Paperwork will be
on site tomorrow.

38:17.380 --> 38:19.029
If it's overtime
for SIX-days

