Blue's class has a--
a field trip

39:08.820 --> 39:10.868
to the children's mu_seum
Wednesday mornIng,

39:10.910 --> 39:13.424
and I was supposed
to be room parent,

39:13.480 --> 39:17.826
but Charley
wants to audition bands

39:17.870 --> 39:19.690
for the Brown Sugar
Festival that day.

39:19.740 --> 39:22.049
Ralph Angel:
I can do it.

39:22.090 --> 39:23.307
Thank you.

39:29.140 --> 39:30.573
What are you doing?

39:30.620 --> 39:32.315
Shh.

39:32.370 --> 39:34.577
Father Julian said you're
not supposed to talk.

39:34.630 --> 39:36.404
Just listen.

