Diagonal?

40:06.050 --> 40:09.008
You good.
Put your hands down.

40:09.050 --> 40:11.962
All right, now take
two small steps
to your left.

40:15.840 --> 40:18.058
[ door opens ]

40:18.110 --> 40:20.010
[ door closes ]

40:31.250 --> 40:32.899
Nova?

40:32.950 --> 40:34.167
I used my key.

40:36.820 --> 40:38.208
Hope that's okay.

40:38.260 --> 40:39.818
Yeah.

40:41.960 --> 40:44.087
Of course it's okay.

40:46.310 --> 40:47.470
Just a bit surprised.

40:50.660 --> 40:52.742
Our last call
was, uh...

40:52.790 --> 40:55.258
Terrible.

40:55.320 --> 40:56.446
That was my fault.

40:59.500 --> 41:01.013
You go through
your whole life

41:01.060 --> 41:05.884
knowing exactly why
you're the way you are.

41:05.940 --> 41:07.840
And then you get one
new piece of the puzzle,

41:07.900 --> 41:09.970
and the whole picture
changes.

41:10.030 --> 41:13.375
Look, if you feel like
I've been pressuring you
or something--

41:13.420 --> 41:14.409
Nova:
We're different.

41:14.470 --> 41:15.812
Very different.

41:17.250 --> 41:19.468
Kind of like
two people I knew.

41:21.820 --> 41:23.811
They were
a special couple.

41:25.610 --> 41:27.123
Everybody said so.

41:29.660 --> 41:33.209
But they let
their differences
keep them apart

41:33.270 --> 41:35.613
for longer
than they should've.

41:39.400 --> 41:40.537
I'm tired...

41:43.280 --> 41:45.748
