inevitable distance

42:26.100 --> 42:27.977
Twisted bitterness

42:28.020 --> 42:31.148
I give her two months,
she'll be over that

42:31.200 --> 42:36.103
'Cause I could walk you
back to the station

42:36.160 --> 42:39.539
Talk about
our own frustrations

42:39.600 --> 42:42.728
'Cause I could walk you
back to the station

42:42.770 --> 42:45.591
